<lb ed="W" n="0352a04"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">錄文三</cb:mulu><head>〔錄文三〕</head>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a06"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a07"/><p xml:id="pW07p0352a0701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">玄奘法師禮拜，逐月有十齋日：</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a08"/><list><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a0801">一<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352001" n="0352001"/>日齋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352002" n="0352002"/>，善惡童子下界，念定光佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a09"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a0901">八日齋，太子下界，念藥師琉璃光佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a10"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1001">十四日齋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352003" n="0352003"/>，司命下界，念賢劫千<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352004" n="0352004"/>佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a11"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1101">十五日齋，五道將軍下界<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352005" n="0352005"/>，念阿彌陀佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a12"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1201">十八日齋，閻羅王天子下界，念地藏菩薩；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a13"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1301">二十<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352006" n="0352006"/>三日齋，天大將軍下界，念大勢至菩薩；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a14"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1401">二十四<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352007" n="0352007"/>日齋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352008" n="0352008"/>，察命下界，念觀世音菩薩；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a15"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1501">二十八日齋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352009" n="0352009"/>，太山府君下界，念盧舍那佛；</item>
<lb ed="W" n="0352a16"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0352a1601">二<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352010" n="0352010"/>十九日齋，四天王下界，念藥王藥上<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0352011" n="0352011"/>菩薩；</item>
<pb ed="W" xml:id="W07.0064c.0353a" n="0353a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0353a01"/><item xml:id="itemW07p0353a0101">三十日<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0353001" n="0353001"/>齋，大<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0353002" n="0353002"/>梵王下界，念釋迦牟尼佛。</item></list>
<lb ed="W" n="0353a02"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0353a03"/><p xml:id="pW07p0353a0301">〔錄文完〕</p></cb:div>
</body>
<back>
