<p>
<note n="0352001" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352001">「一」，底本作「十一」，據甲本刪。</note>
<note n="0352002" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352002">「齋」，底本缺，甲本作「有」，據文意補。</note>
<note n="0352003" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352003">「齋」，底、甲本缺，據文意補。</note>
<note n="0352004" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352004">「千」，甲本作「一千」。</note>
<note n="0352005" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352005">「下界」，底、甲本無，據文意補。</note>
<note n="0352006" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352006">「二十」，底本作「十二」，據甲本改。</note>
<note n="0352007" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352007">「四」，甲本無。</note>
<note n="0352008" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352008">「齋」，底本無。據甲本補。</note>
<note n="0352009" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352009">「齋」，底、甲本無，據文意補。</note>
<note n="0352010" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352010">「二」，甲本作「八」。</note>
<note n="0352011" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0352011">「藥上」，底、甲本無，據文意補。</note>
<note n="0353001" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0353001">「日」，甲本無。</note>
<note n="0353002" resp="#resp44" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0353002">「大」，底、甲本作「念大」，據文意刪。</note>
</p>
